title: Ep195: F**k Me with an F (Ft. Sofia Franklyn)

description:
On this week’s episode, the duo are joined by Sofia Franklyn, host of Sofia with F Podcast. The episode starts with the inevitable conversation regarding Sofia’s departure from the wildly popular podcast Call Her Daddy. The trio quickly jump into ice breakers and asking Sofia if she would rather go to jail or be trapped with her ex in a closet. Mandii shares how she enjoys a good ol finger banging and Weezy shares her love of partying hard and revisits her shared jail experience with Sofia. Tune in to sex tips and more sex stories shared amongst the group!
